### AUTHSUSER-SERVICE ------------------------------------------------

### 회원가입
POST localhost:8081/api/auth/sign-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1234",
  "password": "pwd1234@",
  "role" : "MASTER"
}

### 로그인
POST localhost:8081/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1234",
  "password": "pwd1234@"
}

> {%
  token = response.body.data.token.replace("Bearer ", "");
  client.global.set("token", token);
%}

### 로그아웃
POST localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: {{token}}

### 회원정보 단일검색
